title: No chest with S+

embed.description: Every game is a story; visit the new League of Legends match history to check out how this one ends and share your own!

body: i've been working hard on getting s but now that i have 4 available to earn, i still didnt get one this was a ranked match i got s+ token and such but no key or chest, why is this if it says its available to receive if i make a s- or higher.

replies.body: It looks like you already received a chest for Zyra.  Mastery chests are only one per champion per season, so you'll have to wait until next season to get another chest with her.  Let me know if that clears things up!
wow didn't know that thank you =]
